<h1 id="collaborative-ai:">Collaborative AI:</h1><h1 id="what,-why-and-how?">What, Why and How?</h1><p><br></p><p>AI is the study and design of <strong>intelligent agents.</strong></p><p>Intelligent agents:</p><ul><li>Have own thread of control, continually executing</li><li>Are autonomous</li><li>Exhibit proactive, reactive and social behavior</li><li>Can be physical or virtual, embodied or software-only</li></ul><p><br></p><h2 id="centralized-ai-systems">Centralized AI Systems</h2><p><strong>Centralized </strong>AI system -&gt; <strong>Single-Agent </strong>system</p><p><br></p><p>Centralized <em>computation </em>and <em>control</em></p><p><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></p><p><br></p><p>Distributed <em>computation </em>yet centralized <em>control</em>!</p><p><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></p><p><br></p><h2 id="collaborative-ai-systems">Collaborative AI Systems</h2><p><strong>Collaborative </strong>AI System -&gt; <strong>Multi-Agent </strong>System</p><p><br></p><p>Decentralized <em>computation </em>and <em>control</em></p><p><img src="data:image/png;base64,"></p><p>Collaborative AI is the study and design of multi-agent systems</p><p><br></p><h2 id="why?">Why?</h2><ul><li>Each agent has incomplete information or capabilities for solving a problem</li><li>There is no system for global control</li><li>Data is decentralized</li><li>Computation is asynchronous</li><li>Facilitate <strong>hybrid </strong>(human-AI) intelligence</li><li class="ql-indent-1">Humans assisting machines</li><li class="ql-indent-2">Training, explaining, sustaining</li><li class="ql-indent-1">Machines assisting humans</li><li class="ql-indent-2">Amplifying, interacting, embodying</li></ul>
